Comment: 0,0:00:01.04,0:00:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,845年
Comment: 0,0:00:03.09,0:00:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因突然出現的超大型巨人
Comment: 0,0:00:06.23,0:00:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,和盔甲巨人
Comment: 0,0:00:08.46,0:00:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,日常生活跟著城牆一同被摧毀
Comment: 0,0:00:12.89,0:00:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,然而
Comment: 0,0:00:14.06,0:00:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因從百年飢餓中解放的巨人
Comment: 0,0:00:17.72,0:00:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,人類再度遭到蹂躪
Comment: 0,0:00:20.13,0:00:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,住手!
Comment: 0,0:00:24.14,0:00:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,人類放棄了瑪利亞之牆
Comment: 0,0:00:27.31,0:00:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,失去了兩成的人口與三分之一領土
Comment: 0,0:00:31.21,0:00:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,活動範圍被迫退後至羅塞之牆
Comment: 0,0:00:34.76,0:00:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,OP
Comment: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,太慢了!
Comment: 0,0:02:22.63,0:02:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給我跑!! 一群腦弱!
Comment: 0,0:02:26.30,0:02:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼了! 亞魯雷特
Comment: 0,0:02:28.39,0:02:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你脫隊了喔!
Comment: 0,0:02:30.97,0:02:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,對你來說太重了嗎?
Comment: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,難道只有你要卸下裝備嗎?
Comment: 0,0:02:36.19,0:02:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果這是在戰場上
Comment: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你就在此成了巨人的食物了!
Comment: 0,0:02:42.07,0:02:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可惡...
Comment: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給我
Comment: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣下去會不及格的喔!
Comment: 0,0:02:48.74,0:02:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這次的訓練可是有算分數的
Comment: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣做的話 萊納也會被扣分
Comment: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,盡可能不露餡就好了
Comment: 0,0:02:56.21,0:02:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,趁我還沒改變心意之前
Comment: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,萊納．布朗
Comment: 0,0:03:05.04,0:03:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,擁有強健的體格跟意志力
Comment: 0,0:03:08.13,0:03:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而且獲得同伴們深厚的信賴
Comment: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,說我是累贅... 就算死我也不認
Comment: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏．亞魯雷特
Comment: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,儘管在體力上劣勢
Comment: 0,0:03:24.84,0:03:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是在學科方面卻有著過人的想法
Comment: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮．雷恩哈特
Comment: 0,0:03:46.63,0:03:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,斬擊的切入角度無懈可擊
Comment: 0,0:03:48.80,0:03:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,能夠重創目標
Comment: 0,0:03:50.22,0:03:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,個性有點孤僻
Comment: 0,0:03:51.99,0:03:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,貝爾托特．胡佛
Comment: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,感覺有很高的潛力
Comment: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不過欠缺積極性
Comment: 0,0:03:57.95,0:03:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,約翰．基爾休坦
Comment: 0,0:03:59.73,0:04:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,對於立體機動裝置相當了解
Comment: 0,0:04:01.82,0:04:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不過愛推卸的個性容易與人衝突
Comment: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,雖然斬擊的深度不如她...
Comment: 0,0:04:10.13,0:04:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只好比她早一步來發現巨人了
Comment: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,進入憲兵團的人...
Comment: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,會是我!
Comment: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,謝謝啦! 約翰!
Comment: 0,0:04:24.64,0:04:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,跟在你後面果然是對的!
Comment: 0,0:04:30.26,0:04:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,成功了!
Comment: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,莎夏．布勞斯
Comment: 0,0:04:35.36,0:04:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有不輸任何人的直覺
Comment: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因此 不適合團體行動
Comment: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,柯尼．史普林格
Comment: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,擅長小區域的機動
Comment: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不過腦袋有點不太靈光
Comment: 0,0:04:47.92,0:04:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要來囉!
Comment: 0,0:04:57.37,0:04:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可惡! 又比米卡莎還要淺!
Comment: 0,0:05:00.47,0:05:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎．阿卡曼
Comment: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,擁有通過任何困難科目的執行力
Comment: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要說她是歷代難見的人才 給她最高的評價也不為過
Comment: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連．葉卡
Comment: 0,0:05:10.50,0:05:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,雖然沒有特別的才能
Comment: 0,0:05:12.06,0:05:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但憑著努力讓成績逐漸攀升
Comment: 0,0:05:15.47,0:05:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還有...
Comment: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,比其他人更想達成目標的意識
Comment: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好痛...
Comment: 0,0:05:38.26,0:05:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,抱歉 我不太會控制力氣
Comment: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這次該你當壞人了
Comment: 0,0:05:47.08,0:05:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼了?
Comment: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼說 這個訓練到底...
Comment: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要士兵把人當作對手到底要幹嘛?
Comment: 0,0:05:55.21,0:05:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,用空手對付獵物
Comment: 0,0:05:57.42,0:05:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,根本是智障的行為
Comment: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你這叫不負責任呢
Comment: 0,0:06:04.35,0:06:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們是士兵對吧
Comment: 0,0:06:06.31,0:06:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,再怎麼不利的狀況下
Comment: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也會有不能逃走的時候
Comment: 0,0:06:10.61,0:06:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不管對方是什麼東西
Comment: 0,0:06:12.49,0:06:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,都必須學到能自由運用大砲或格鬥術
Comment: 0,0:06:16.99,0:06:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣才是擁有力量的士兵 該有的責任
Comment: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,說到這 你看
Comment: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,啊... 亞妮啊
Comment: 0,0:06:29.31,0:06:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,又趁教官沒發現的時候摸魚了
Comment: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,來唷 艾連
Comment: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,去教訓那個打混的傢伙
Comment: 0,0:06:36.52,0:06:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,教教她身為士兵應該做哪些事
Comment: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,蛤?
Comment: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,討厭被教官用頭撞嗎?
Comment: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果不希望再變矮
Comment: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳就給我想起來剛來到這裡的時候 認真一點
Comment: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂 你這話是什麼意思?
Comment: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,非常生氣呢
Comment: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,一直以來都覺得很可怕
Comment: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是真生氣起來真的很嚇人
Comment: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那麼
Comment: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,開始囉 艾連
Comment: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我來?
Comment: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮 妳應該知道怎麼做吧?
Comment: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要上囉!
Comment: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,什... 什麼?
Comment: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我的腳被踢到了嗎!?
Comment: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,痛...
Comment: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我可以走了嗎?
Comment: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還沒 還有短刀訓練
Comment: 0,0:07:35.48,0:07:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,等一下 亞妮
Comment: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這也是有標準程序的...
Comment: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,接著
Comment: 0,0:07:49.09,0:07:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,接下來輪到你來襲擊我了吧
Comment: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不 不是... 我...
Comment: 0,0:07:54.17,0:07:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給我上喔 萊納
Comment: 0,0:07:56.43,0:07:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不是要將做為士兵的責任
Comment: 0,0:07:58.47,0:07:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,告訴她嗎?
Comment: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是呀...
Comment: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,士兵有不能退縮的情況
Comment: 0,0:08:08.66,0:08:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在就是!
Comment: 0,0:08:15.50,0:08:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真厲害的技巧
Comment: 0,0:08:17.52,0:08:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是從誰那學到的呢?
Comment: 0,0:08:19.96,0:08:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,從我爸那
Comment: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你爸爸將這技巧...
Comment: 0,0:08:23.04,0:08:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎樣都好
Comment: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,做這樣的事根本沒有意義
Comment: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你是指這個訓練嗎?
Comment: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,對人格鬥術並不會計算分數
Comment: 0,0:08:34.35,0:08:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,一般都會那樣隨便混過
Comment: 0,0:08:37.36,0:08:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,能進入憲兵團
Comment: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,到內地獲得權力的
Comment: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只有成績前十名而已
Comment: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真正認真在練習的
Comment: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就只有你們這種老實笨蛋了
Comment: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,或是真的笨蛋
Comment: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,夭壽! 是教官!
Comment: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要說為什麼的話這世界上
Comment: 0,0:08:57.50,0:09:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,越是有力量對抗巨人的人
Comment: 0,0:09:00.13,0:09:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就能夠離巨人越遠
Comment: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你覺得為什麼會如此可笑呢?
Comment: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,誰知道... 到底為什麼呢!
Comment: 0,0:09:12.45,0:09:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那是因為...
Comment: 0,0:09:14.16,0:09:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,人的本質
Comment: 0,0:09:22.94,0:09:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,無論如何我...
Comment: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,絕不可能會成為在這無聊的世界上
Comment: 0,0:09:29.01,0:09:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,玩士兵遊戲的笨蛋
Comment: 0,0:09:33.56,0:09:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,看來妳從頭到腳都不適合當士兵
Comment: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因為太熱衷於變強沒有注意到
Comment: 0,0:09:42.09,0:09:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這麼簡單的矛盾
Comment: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,他們是為了逃離巨人而學習擊敗巨人的技術
Comment: 0,0:09:55.56,0:09:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這也沒辦法呀
Comment: 0,0:09:57.36,0:09:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在瑪利亞之牆被破壞前的立體機動術
Comment: 0,0:10:00.19,0:10:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只有人數較少的調查軍團才需要
Comment: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:06.50,Upside,,0,0,0,karaoke,因此立體機動術才會沒落
Comment: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:08.15,Upside,,0,0,0,karaoke,所以...
Comment: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只要有一瞬間保有自己的夢想也好
Comment: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣一來 就能利用他們感性的地方
Comment: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,多少消耗掉了一些廢物
Comment: 0,0:10:11.48,0:10:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,說簡單一點啦
Comment: 0,0:10:13.35,0:10:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就是啊 不是誰都能做的呢
Comment: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,聽我說這句話你們不會吃虧 如果想進入憲兵團的話
Comment: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,能進就好了 能在國王身邊做事
Comment: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒有比這還要來得光榮了
Comment: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂 馬可
Comment: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你還是老實說吧 你真正的想法
Comment: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,進入憲兵團是因為
Comment: 0,0:10:37.52,0:10:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在內地那種安全舒適的過日子 等著我們才對吧
Comment: 0,0:10:41.17,0:10:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼會 至少我不...
Comment: 0,0:10:43.23,0:10:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你說內地很舒適?
Comment: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這裡五年前也是內地啊
Comment: 0,0:10:50.43,0:10:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你到底想說什麼?
Comment: 0,0:10:52.28,0:10:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:10:54.49,0:10:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,約翰 就算你不去內地
Comment: 0,0:10:57.88,0:11:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你的腦子裡應該也夠舒服了吧?
Comment: 0,0:11:03.65,0:11:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你這傢伙...
Comment: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你不覺得奇怪嗎?
Comment: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為了遠離巨人而學習斬殺巨人的技術的這種體系
Comment: 0,0:11:12.01,0:11:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,事到如今是在說什麼
Comment: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為了我的自己
Comment: 0,0:11:15.12,0:11:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也該繼續維持這種愚蠢的政策
Comment: 0,0:11:17.68,0:11:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你這混蛋傢伙!
Comment: 0,0:11:18.79,0:11:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,吵死了 這就是現實!
Comment: 0,0:11:20.71,0:11:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連... 住手啦
Comment: 0,0:11:22.46,0:11:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,都住手
Comment: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你他媽的別開玩笑了!!
Comment: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,放手啊! 衣服會破掉的啊!!
Comment: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,衣服不是重點吧!! 羨慕死我了!
Comment: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,蛤? 你在說什麼啊?
Comment: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,對了... 其實他...
Comment: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就只是在抒發情緒...
Comment: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,跟之前的我一樣...
Comment: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而我已經不一樣了...
Comment: 0,0:11:56.53,0:11:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,使用學到的技術
Comment: 0,0:11:57.80,0:11:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就這樣壓制住他!
Comment: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,痛...
Comment: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你剛剛做了什麼!
Comment: 0,0:12:12.17,0:12:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是在你們打混摸魚的時候 我千辛萬苦學會的格鬥術
Comment: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,放任情緒去活才是現實?
Comment: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你這樣子...
Comment: 0,0:12:25.07,0:12:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還算是士兵嗎?
Comment: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我剛才聽見很大聲的聲音...
Comment: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有誰可以說明一下嗎?
Comment: 0,0:12:47.31,0:12:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那是莎夏放屁的聲音
Comment: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,欸?!
Comment: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,又是妳啊...
Comment: 0,0:12:53.38,0:12:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,請注意妳的行為!
Comment: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,接著 218名訓練兵迎接了畢業
Comment: 0,0:13:12.93,0:13:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,獻出你們的心臟吧!!
Comment: 0,0:13:14.55,0:13:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是!!
Comment: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,今天以訓練兵身份畢業的諸位
Comment: 0,0:13:20.31,0:13:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,將有三個選擇
Comment: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,負責強化城牆 防守各城市的「駐紮軍團」
Comment: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,抱著必死決心 挑戰牆外巨人領域的「調查軍團」
Comment: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,以及在國王身邊管理人民 維持秩序的「憲兵團」
Comment: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,當然 新兵可以加入憲兵團的
Comment: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,僅限於剛剛發表成績在前十名的人
Comment: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,終於走到這步了...
Comment: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,輪到我們人類了...
Comment: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這回要把巨人殺光殆盡
Comment: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,CM
Comment: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,太好了 這樣我也會進憲兵團了
Comment: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,已經不用再為食物煩惱了
Comment: 0,0:14:19.31,0:14:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼我的排名會比艾連還後面
Comment: 0,0:14:22.36,0:14:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,該死!
Comment: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你說你不進去憲兵團?
Comment: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你是認真的嗎? 艾連
Comment: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好不容易才擠進前十名的耶
Comment: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是一開始就決定好的事
Comment: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我來受訓練並不是為了到內地生活
Comment: 0,0:14:36.72,0:14:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是為了要和巨人戰鬥
Comment: 0,0:14:38.95,0:14:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼可能贏得了啊!
Comment: 0,0:14:44.58,0:14:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你們也知道的吧
Comment: 0,0:14:46.64,0:14:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,至今為止有幾萬人被吃了
Comment: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,失去了總人口的兩成以上
Comment: 0,0:14:50.84,0:14:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,答案已經很明顯了
Comment: 0,0:14:53.54,0:14:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,人類是...
Comment: 0,0:14:55.57,0:14:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,贏不了巨人的
Comment: 0,0:15:03.15,0:15:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,所以呢...
Comment: 0,0:15:06.15,0:15:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,認為贏不了就要放棄了嗎?
Comment: 0,0:15:10.21,0:15:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,的確...
Comment: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,人類一路敗亡到現在
Comment: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那是因為對巨人的無知
Comment: 0,0:15:17.28,0:15:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,對抗巨人用數量取勝是沒有意義的
Comment: 0,0:15:20.34,0:15:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,雖然輸了
Comment: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是戰鬥所獲得的情報
Comment: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,確實是連結著未來的希望
Comment: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,難道要放棄我們幾十萬人的犧牲
Comment: 0,0:15:28.06,0:15:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,所換來的戰術上的進步
Comment: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,然後乖乖地去當巨人的食物嗎?
Comment: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,別開玩笑了!
Comment: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我要把...
Comment: 0,0:15:36.21,0:15:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,巨人一隻不留地殺光
Comment: 0,0:15:38.61,0:15:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,然後離開這個狹小的牆內世界
Comment: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這就是我的夢想
Comment: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,人類還沒真的輸!
Comment: 0,0:15:54.53,0:15:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,等一下啊 艾連!
Comment: 0,0:15:57.02,0:15:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只要還活著 不論是牆外還是哪裡我都能去
Comment: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我絕對要進入憲兵團
Comment: 0,0:16:13.35,0:16:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:16:14.67,0:16:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,關於剛剛說的夢想...
Comment: 0,0:16:17.63,0:16:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是模仿你之前說的
Comment: 0,0:16:19.30,0:16:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,並非往牆內而是牆外
Comment: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我要進入調查軍團
Comment: 0,0:16:27.18,0:16:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏你是認真的嗎!?
Comment: 0,0:16:29.06,0:16:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你的學科成績是第一名 該好好活用這點
Comment: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我就算死了也不想成為累贅
Comment: 0,0:16:35.94,0:16:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我也要進入調查軍團
Comment: 0,0:16:38.45,0:16:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂
Comment: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳是首席欸
Comment: 0,0:16:40.51,0:16:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給我進入憲兵團
Comment: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果你要進入憲兵團的話
Comment: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那我也跟你去憲兵團
Comment: 0,0:16:47.54,0:16:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要是你要去駐紮軍團的話
Comment: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那麼我也會這樣做
Comment: 0,0:16:52.23,0:16:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果艾連不在我身邊
Comment: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,一定會早死的
Comment: 0,0:16:57.03,0:16:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那種事我才沒拜託過妳
Comment: 0,0:17:00.15,0:17:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我不想再失去親人了
Comment: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,來了!!
Comment: 0,0:17:26.67,0:17:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是調查軍團的主力部隊!
Comment: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾爾文團長!
Comment: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,請你們把巨人全都殺光!
Comment: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你們看!
Comment: 0,0:17:34.39,0:17:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是里維士官長!
Comment: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,一個人的戰力就抵得過一個旅團呢!
Comment: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,呿!
Comment: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,煩死人了...
Comment: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,跟五年前比起來完全不一樣了呢
Comment: 0,0:17:44.82,0:17:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,調查軍團中竟然有這麼多人受到期待
Comment: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,大家的氣氛已經變得很開朗了
Comment: 0,0:17:51.16,0:17:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,已經五年沒發生什麼事了
Comment: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,固定砲塔也已經改良過了呢
Comment: 0,0:17:55.91,0:17:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,超大型巨人應該是不會再來了吧
Comment: 0,0:17:58.39,0:17:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也是呢
Comment: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在說什麼啊!
Comment: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你們這對笨蛋夫妻
Comment: 0,0:18:02.38,0:18:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,哪有 什麼很相配的夫妻什麼的...
Comment: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你太心急了吧 艾連
Comment: 0,0:18:08.01,0:18:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,唷! 你們幾個
Comment: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,漢尼斯先生
Comment: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,聽說你們幾個昨天畢業啦
Comment: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,當時的小屁孩 還真是了不起呢
Comment: 0,0:18:18.35,0:18:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,漢尼斯先生才是
Comment: 0,0:18:20.01,0:18:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,已經喝醉喝到隊長了
Comment: 0,0:18:22.50,0:18:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你這傢伙...
Comment: 0,0:18:26.06,0:18:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真是對不起
Comment: 0,0:18:27.85,0:18:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒能救到你媽媽
Comment: 0,0:18:32.14,0:18:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那不是漢尼斯先生的錯
Comment: 0,0:18:35.27,0:18:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們已經不再無知了
Comment: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,已經不會再讓那種悲傷的事發生了
Comment: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,絕對要戰勝巨人
Comment: 0,0:18:47.87,0:18:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,該說是為了他的成長而高興嗎...?
Comment: 0,0:18:52.37,0:18:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可別死了啊
Comment: 0,0:18:56.02,0:18:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,蛤?
Comment: 0,0:18:57.33,0:18:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你說你要進入調查軍團?
Comment: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,柯尼...
Comment: 0,0:19:00.25,0:19:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你之前不是說要加入憲兵團...
Comment: 0,0:19:02.65,0:19:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是沒錯啦...
Comment: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只是...
Comment: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好像是受了艾連昨天的演說的影響呢
Comment: 0,0:19:08.10,0:19:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,啊?
Comment: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,吵死了!
Comment: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是我自己決定的啦
Comment: 0,0:19:13.70,0:19:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,幹嘛害羞啊
Comment: 0,0:19:15.97,0:19:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,又不是只有你
Comment: 0,0:19:19.61,0:19:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,托瑪斯
Comment: 0,0:19:20.85,0:19:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,難道說...
Comment: 0,0:19:22.15,0:19:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那個... 各位
Comment: 0,0:19:24.86,0:19:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我從長官的糧食庫偷來了一些肉
Comment: 0,0:19:29.74,0:19:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,莎夏 妳想被關禁閉嗎!?
Comment: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳真的是個笨蛋啊...
Comment: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,笨蛋好可怕啊...
Comment: 0,0:19:35.78,0:19:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,待會我們大家分著吃吧
Comment: 0,0:19:38.41,0:19:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,把它切片夾麵包..
Comment: 0,0:19:40.66,0:19:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,呵呵呵呵呵呵...
Comment: 0,0:19:41.62,0:19:42.78,Upside,,0,0,0,karaoke,呵呵呵呵呵...
Comment: 0,0:19:41.62,0:19:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快點放回去啦!
Comment: 0,0:19:42.71,0:19:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就是啊
Comment: 0,0:19:44.01,0:19:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,領土變小之後 肉可是變得特別貴重呢
Comment: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,放心啦
Comment: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只要把土地搶回來
Comment: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,牛羊也會跟著增加啊
Comment: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我也要吃那塊肉!
Comment: 0,0:20:04.41,0:20:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我也要吃 幫我留一點
Comment: 0,0:20:07.66,0:20:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,當然 我也要
Comment: 0,0:20:10.05,0:20:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你們...
Comment: 0,0:20:11.86,0:20:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連你還杵在這裡幹嘛
Comment: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不快回去工作的話
Comment: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,會被發現喔
Comment: 0,0:20:16.85,0:20:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,午餐時間還沒到哦
Comment: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,距離那時已經五年了...
Comment: 0,0:20:28.40,0:20:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,人類終於逐漸找回了尊嚴
Comment: 0,0:20:33.78,0:20:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,能贏的贏的!
Comment: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,人類的反擊...
Comment: 0,0:20:40.70,0:20:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,將從現在開始
Comment: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好燙...
Comment: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼了!?
Comment: 0,0:21:12.52,0:21:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,山姆耶爾!!
Comment: 0,0:21:14.78,0:21:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,莎夏!
Comment: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,山姆耶爾! 你不要亂動喔
Comment: 0,0:21:27.90,0:21:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好險啊...
Comment: 0,0:21:32.47,0:21:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,牆壁被破壞了...
Comment: 0,0:21:36.55,0:21:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,又來了...
Comment: 0,0:21:37.80,0:21:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,巨人 又要闖進來了!
Comment: 0,0:21:44.11,0:21:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,全部都殺光 一隻不留地
Comment: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,一隻不留地...
Comment: 0,0:21:55.87,0:21:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,固定砲整備四班!
Comment: 0,0:21:57.85,0:21:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,準備戰鬥!!
Comment: 0,0:22:00.54,0:22:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,目標就在眼前!
Comment: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,超大型巨人!!
Comment: 0,0:22:03.51,0:22:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是絕佳的機會!
Comment: 0,0:22:04.85,0:22:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,絕對不要讓他給跑了!!
Comment: 0,0:22:16.21,0:22:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,唷!
Comment: 0,0:22:19.03,0:22:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,五年沒見了啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Comment: 0,0:23:56.68,0:23:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,地獄再次張開了大口
Comment: 0,0:24:00.22,0:24:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,連喘息的時間都沒有
Comment: 0,0:24:01.90,0:24:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就被巨人吃掉的士兵們
Comment: 0,0:24:04.73,0:24:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在這之中
Comment: 0,0:24:06.12,0:24:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連能否將在死亡深淵中的阿爾敏給救出來呢?
