Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.37,0:03:18.09,SP-EG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Was it shocking for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:19.70,SP-EG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Something is scaring you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:21.37,SP-EG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}The enemy will hunt you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.37,0:03:22.84,SP-EG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}No matter what you do
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:24.66,SP-EG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}But we're gonna fight for you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.92,0:03:26.57,SP-EG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Til we defeat them all
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:28.46,SP-EG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}If not... there's no way out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.46,0:03:31.75,SP-EG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Keep your weapons aimed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:34.99,SP-EG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Here comes the chilling face
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:38.52,SP-EG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Push down your fear
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:42.66,SP-EG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Jump on the necks of the monsters
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:44.69,SP-EG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}You can't hide your self
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.69,0:03:46.17,SP-EG,,0,0,0,,You can't run
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.59,0:03:49.87,SP-EG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}We're fighting for our lives
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:53.25,SP-EG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}And we just can not lose again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:55.33,SP-EG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}There's not much time
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.39,0:03:57.07,SP-EG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Be ready to fight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:03:58.13,SP-EG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.37,0:03:18.09,SP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}你對此感到震驚嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:19.70,SP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}有什麼東西嚇到你嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:21.37,SP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}敵人會追殺你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.37,0:03:22.84,SP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}不論你採取什麼行動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:24.66,SP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}但是我們會為你而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.92,0:03:26.57,SP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}直到我們打敗他們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:28.46,SP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}如果失敗...就無路可逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.46,0:03:31.75,SP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}保持你的武器對準目標
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:34.99,SP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}戰慄的臉迎面襲來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:38.52,SP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}壓抑你的恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:42.66,SP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}跳到這些怪物的後頸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:44.69,SP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}你無處可躲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.69,0:03:46.17,SP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}無處可逃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.59,0:03:49.87,SP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}我們在為生存而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:53.25,SP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}而且我們非贏不可
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:55.33,SP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}時間緊迫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.39,0:03:57.07,SP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}準備戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:03:58.13,SP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}上吧!
